<ARCH_SCAN_V3>
@ID: AUTHORIZATION_MODEL_AUDIT
@GOAL: EVALUATE_STRICTNESS_OF_ACCESS_CONTROL_LOGIC_AND_PERMISSION_MAPPING
@PARENT_CONTEXT: identity_mapping.protocol, privilege_transitions.protocol

<GLOBAL_VARS>
# Типы моделей авторизации
RBAC_MARKERS: "(@Role|hasRole|checkRole|user\.role|roles\.includes)"
ABAC_MARKERS: "(@Attribute|checkPolicy|policy\.enforce|context\.attributes)"
ACL_MARKERS: "(getPermissions|checkAccess|acl\.can|hasPermission)"

# Опасные паттерны "Вседозволенности"
WILDCARD_PERMS: "('*'|'all'|'any'|'root')"
BYPASS_LOGIC: "(is_admin\s?==\s?true|isAdmin|skipAuthz|disableACL)"
</GLOBAL_VARS>

<CONTEXT_MAP>
[AUTHZ_ENGINE] <- {path: (authz|policy|guard|access-control), match: ({{RBAC_MARKERS}}|{{ABAC_MARKERS}})}
[SECURE_RESOURCE] <- {match: {{SENSITIVE_ACTIONS}}, layer: [APP]}
[PERMISSION_MAP] <- {path: (config|seed|migration), match: (permissions|roles|grants)}
</CONTEXT_MAP>

<ASSERTIONS>
# Логические инварианты модели авторизации
! ([SECURE_RESOURCE]) & !([AUTHZ_ENGINE]) : "CRITICAL: Sensitive operation has no associated authorization check."
! ({{WILDCARD_PERMS}} -> [ZONE_EXT]) : "HIGH: Wildcard permissions assigned to external/low-trust entities."
? ({{RBAC_MARKERS}} -> !{{OWNER_CHECKS}}) : "HIGH: RBAC used without Ownership check. High risk of BOLA/IDOR (User A accessing User B's data)."
! ({{BYPASS_LOGIC}}) : "MEDIUM: Hardcoded admin bypass or 'skip' flags detected in authorization flow."
</ASSERTIONS>

<EXECUTION_PIPELINE>
1. MODEL_IDENTIFICATION:
   - Determine the primary AuthZ model: RBAC (Role-based), ABAC (Attribute-based), or ACL. [cite: 13]
   - Map how roles/permissions are linked to [SECURE_RESOURCE]. [cite: 13]
2. GRANULARITY_CHECK:
   - Analyze if the system distinguishes between "Action" (can delete) and "Scope" (can delete *my* record vs *any* record). [cite: 14]
   - Flag "Coarse-grained" AuthZ where a single 'user' role grants excessive access. [cite: 4]
3. INHERITANCE_AUDIT:
   - Check for Role Hierarchy (e.g., Manager inherits User). [cite: 1, 13]
   - Ensure "Shadow Permissions" are not accidentally granted through complex inheritance. 
4. STATIC_PERMISSION_SCAN:
   - Review [PERMISSION_MAP] files (YAML/JSON/DB Seeds). [cite: 29]
   - Look for over-privileged default roles. 
5. DYNAMIC_POLICY_INTEGRITY:
   - For ABAC: Verify that attributes (like `department_id`) are fetched from a secure [ID_STORE] and cannot be manipulated via [INPUT_SOURCES]. [cite: 52, 61]
</EXECUTION_PIPELINE>

<OUTPUT_SPEC>
GENERATE_AUTHZ_MODEL_REPORT:
  - MODEL_TYPE | GRANULARITY_LEVEL | IDENTIFIED_ROLES | MISSING_OWNERSHIP_CHECKS
VISUALIZE: "Mermaid graph: Role-Permission Matrix or Policy Tree."
FILTER: RISK >= MEDIUM
</OUTPUT_SPEC>
</ARCH_SCAN_V3>